The evidence with the title 'GOP's obamacare replacement bill: here are the winners and losers ' says Mar 7, 2017  ... Under the GOP plan : refundable tax credits are based on your age and get phased out if you earn more than $ 75,000 year, starting at $2,000 annually for individuals intheir 20s , and up to $ 4,000 for those in their 60s. For a household with multiple adults , the maximum tax credit would be $14,000 a year. 
